title: Boxer Dog Snuggles Up To Her New Human Baby Brother
text:
Boxer Dog Snuggles Up To Her New Human Baby Brother Subscribe to Reshareworthy! It's FREE and always will be! 
When it comes to cuddling, Astrid the Boxer dog has it down to a science. And when it comes to her new little human, the Swedish dog is all affection. “She is an energetic dog who loves people especially kids,” her family writes. “She is really sweet and protective of this new pack member.”
